Class CertificationGroup

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject, sailpoint.tools.xml.XMLReferenceTarget
public class CertificationGroup
extends SailPointObject

Represents a grouping of Certification objects. Most commonly, this is used to group together all the access reviews generated for a given certification schedule execution.
